## UI Component Rules

- Use shadcn components for building UI interfaces
- Use lucide-react for all icon implementations
- Use the navigate function from '@/lib/routes/routes.util' for all navigation links
- Prefer colors defined in /src/app/globals.css or /src/styles/tailwind.theme.css for consistency
- Maintain consistent spacing using TailwindCSS utility classes
- Ensure components are responsive: min-768px
